[[绿色革命|绿色革命]]带来的农业工业化使得食物增产，随之而来的是1950年人口暴增（超过每年1.8%）。<ref name="The limits of a Green Revolution">"[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_depth/6496585.stm The limits of a Green Revolution?] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_depth/6496585.stm |date=20110728055441 }}". BBC News. 29 March 2007.</ref>人口增长率在1964年达到每年2.1%的峰值。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://esa.un.org/unpd/wpp/Analytical-Figures/htm/fig_6.htm |title=United Nations, United Nations, Department of Economic and Social Affairs, Population Division (2011): World Population Prospects: The 2010 Revision |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512065842/http://esa.un.org/unpd/wpp/Analytical-Figures/htm/fig_6.htm |archivedate=2011-05-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>例如，[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]人口从1961年的9700万增至2010年的2亿3760万，<ref>{{Cite news |author=Widjojo Nitisastro |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RQbd3-G6riUC&pg=&dq&hl=en#v=onepage&q=&f=false |title=Population Trends in Indonesia |publisher=Equinox Publishing |accessdate=2011-11-06 |year=2006 |page=268 |isbn=979-3780-43-6 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922130058/https://books.google.com/books?id=RQbd3-G6riUC&pg=&dq&hl=en#v=onepage&q=&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bps.go.id/65tahun/SP2010_agregat_data_perProvinsi.pdf |title=Central Bureau of Statistics: ''Census 2010'' |publisher=Badan Pusat Statistik |accessdate=2011-01-17 |language=id |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101113144717/http://www.bps.go.id/65tahun/SP2010_agregat_data_perProvinsi.pdf |archivedate=2010-11-13 }}</ref>49年间增长145%。在[[印度|印度]]，人口从1951年的3亿6110万增至2011年的12亿，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indiabudget.nic.in/es2006-07/chapt2007/tab97.pdf|title=Census Population|work=Census of India|publisher=Ministry of Finance India|accessdate=2008-12-18|format=PDF|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219073658/http://indiabudget.nic.in/es2006-07/chapt2007/tab97.pdf|archive-date=2008-12-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|year=2011|title=Provisional Population Totals – Census 2011|work=Office of the Registrar General and Census Commissioner|publisher=[[Ministry_of_Home_Affairs_(India)|Ministry of Home Affairs]], Government of India|url=http://www.censusindia.gov.in/2011-prov-results/indiaatglance.html|accessdate=2011-03-29|ref={{Sfnref|Ministry of Home Affairs|2011}}|journal=|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224183749/http://www.censusindia.gov.in/2011-prov-results/indiaatglance.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>60年增长235%。

